title: Cancellation Day
itunes:title: Cancellation Day
description:
Good evening and welcome to Nighty Night with Rabia Chaudy: Bedtime Stories To Keep You Awake. Tonight's tale is about a contest where if you win, the only thing you receive...is death. Please enjoy, Cancellation Day.

Tonight's tale is written by Will Rogers. 

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
